ğŸ§© Key Functions

1. Off-Chain Lineage

Each verified integrity_manifest.json and lineage.merkle.json is uploaded to IPFS or Arweave.

The resulting CID (content identifier) is recorded in a new file: interplanetary_links.json.



2. Immutable Reference Chain

Every CID is hashed and appended to a new rolling ledger planetary_chain.json, producing a continuous on-chain checksum history.



3. Cross-Ledger Attestation

Optional Ethereum / Bitcoin / Filecoin transaction hashes can be stored under

"anchors": { "ethereum_tx": "", "bitcoin_tx": "", "filecoin_cid": "" }

to prove persistence across multiple ecosystems.



4. Federated Replication

Each node can pin another nodeâ€™s CIDs, ensuring redundancy across continents.





