ğŸ§  Integration Command

Add to scripts/orchestrator.py:

elif args.cmd == "ipfs":
    import subprocess, json, datetime
    files = ["integrity_manifest.json","lineage.merkle.json"]
    links = {}
    for f in files:
        cid = subprocess.check_output(["ipfs","add","-Q",f]).decode().strip()
        links["cid_"+f.split('.')[0]] = cid
    obj = {
        "version":"v150",
        "generated_utc": datetime.datetime.utcnow().isoformat()+"Z",
        **links
    }
    json.dump(obj, open("interplanetary_links.json","w"), indent=2)
    print(json.dumps(obj, indent=2))

Usage:

python3 scripts/orchestrator.py ipfs


